headline: NetApp to Participate in J. P. Morgan’s CEO Spotlight Series to Discuss Industry Dynamics Related to AI Opportunities
summary: SAN JOSE, Calif., September 04, 2025--George Kurian, chief executive officer at NetApp (NASDAQ: NTAP) will participate in J. P. Morgan’s CEO Spotlight Series to discuss long-term strategies and roadmaps pertaining to broader industry AI dynamics, as well as specific drivers and opportunities for NetApp. Interested parties can find more information on NetApp’s Investor Relations website at http://investors.netapp.com.

headline: NetApp Up 14% in a Month: How Should Investors Play the Stock?
summary: NTAP's shares surges 14% in a month as flash, cloud and AI growth fuel optimism, but macro headwinds raise caution for investors.
